### Login success
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123!"
}

### Login failure
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### Authorization header example
# Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
